reviewText: Lots of information on the Bank and those behind the scenes making the Band AC/Dc a great success
It's great to look and see
I was disappointed that it was not approved by the band. Wish I would have seen that before ordering. Don't expect amazon to put products for sale that aren't approved.

overall, I was disapointed in the fact that its mostly talking heads, sutting stationary and speaking of their opinions on the band. Offering little facts and no "real" appearances from the actual band members. Basically, don't waste your money!!
im AC/DC fan and this is awsome to have :-)
